      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "Z-IMAGE + CONTROLNET - structure-controlled generation (local)\n\nLock the COMPOSITION (pose / depth / edges) of a source image, then\ngenerate something new that follows that structure.\n\nHOW:\n  1. Load a control-source image (bottom-left).\n  2. AIO_Preprocessor extracts the control map. Pick the type:\n       CannyEdgePreprocessor      = outlines (default, no extra download)\n       DepthAnythingV2Preprocessor= depth (downloads a small model 1st run)\n       DWPreprocessor / OpenposePreprocessor = body pose\n  3. Write your prompt. Run.\n\nSTRENGTH (ZImageFunControlnet): 0.6-1.0. Lower=looser, higher=stricter.\nUses Z-Image Fun ControlNet via ModelPatchLoader (in models/model_patches)\n+ ZImageFunControlnet - NOT the normal ControlNet nodes. Steps 8 / CFG 1."
      ],
      "color": "#443322",
      "bgcolor": "#443322"
